Execute a CDO operation

cdo_execute.Rd

Execute a CDO operation

Usage

cdo_execute(
  operation,
  output = temp_output(operation),
  options = NULL,
  verbose = FALSE
)

Arguments

operation

a CDO operation

output

an output file or base string for output files. Defaults to temporary files.

options

character vector with CDO options.

verbose

whether to print the command being executed.
